<p>In a series of posts shared to her Instagram Story, the 51-year-old wrote that she 'actually has respect' for Fox for 'living her life for herself' and moving on with Kelly. </p>

<p>She added: 'Megan finally living her life for herself is in itself a gift to her children.'</p>

